OL,4,Cconstruction workers to ballot for
OL,5,Cstrike action
OL,7,FUnite said the dispute is over demands
OL,8,Ffor better work conditions, involving
OL,9,Fworkers such as electricians, joiners,
OL,10,Fpipefitters, riggers, groundworkers,
OL,11,Fwelders and painters.
OL,13,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,14,Fsaid: "Our members are highly skilled
OL,15,Fand operate in an extremely
OL,16,Fchallenging and hazardous environment.
OL,18,F"Despite this, construction employers
OL,19,Fare refusing to pay an allowance for
OL,20,Four members' skills and dedication."
