OL,7,FUnite regional officer Ryan Armstrong
OL,8,Fadded: "There is still time to avoid
OL,9,Fstrike action but the employers must
OL,10,Freturn to the table with a viable
OL,11,Foffer."
OL,13,FA Sellafield spokesperson said: "We
OL,14,Fare aware of a dispute involving
OL,15,Fcontractors working at Sellafield
OL,16,Femployed under the NAECI and CIJC
OL,17,FWorking Rule Agreements.
